e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成世比港女食住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"認真的，本人就有一位同事唔靚極肥，但唔係好女仔。性格有問題。<br />\n當然人無完美，生得唔靚可能就會令佢成長有多啲阻滯，但比較返我人生中遇過生得唔靚嘅女性朋友，真係冇一個好似佢咁衰。<br />\n<br />\n雖然都有一啲女士可能生得靚,成日畀人遷就，變得嬌生慣讓。但係我又諗返自己識嘅靚女，甚至女神級嘅靚女，性格都好好架喎（只係有部分,唔係全部）<br />\n<br />\n總之，生得靚唔靚，同性格好唔好<br />\n無必然關係"},{"pid":"6e6d089a47c7b3bac04cd48674d7232f3cd594e3","tid":2211001,"uid":121291,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"唔關樣事<br />\n曾經識得個又肥又醜又矮性格有問題<br />\n心地又唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而識得好多靚女份人都唔錯"},{"pid":"92e7c38444b757e9bea13d03bd1d543cdf92a193","tid":2211001,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:31:48.000Z","msg":"心地好壞同外表唔係反比㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識唔少靚女好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肥柒閪撚到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c781b0aec1b8298042bc7ff8ea36483c54943ea0","tid":2211001,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"樣衰好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faefd39fcfa0df16298d75a57ae685cf562ae6d","tid":2211001,"uid":271397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:36:21.000Z","msg":"除非屋企人好識教, 否則靚女通常都係比較少同理心, 又缺乏幽默感"},{"pid":"db1cb86eb84bae529b43a4df87e773ea50d83b03","tid":2211001,"uid":73989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:38:50.000Z","msg":"TB點計"},{"pid":"ec36c9162665fc2df337a220fc8dc13860360d2d","tid":2211001,"uid":271397,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"如果一條女(其實男